      This section can showcase real patient cases, including cosmetic and restorative treatments, once photos are ready.
    </p>

    <h2>Real Results, Real Patients</h2>
    <p>
      Our goal is to create natural, confident smiles that fit each patient’s unique features and preferences.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
